				<td colspan="2"><span>
<br />

<br />
Again the biggest reason DotB is worth so much is not
<br />
the .2 mod increase from selo's drums of the march.
<br />

<br />
It is the simple fact that it is primary equippable.
<br />
This means you can weild the drums in primary while
<br />
having your epic or other weapon in secondary.
<br />

<br />
Say you have 2 weapons equipped, and the drums on your
<br />
cursor.  You start to sing a percussion based song, and
<br />
right before the casting time is over, you click in your drums.
<br />
You get full 2.8 mod effect on song.  Now you click out your
<br />
drums and continue to melee.  You don't even miss a round
<br />
of melee, and you get full percussion bonus to your song.
<br />
That is why the DotB is worth so much, and it's worth getting.
<br />

<br />
Astuce Subterfuge
<br />
65 Bard
<br />
innoruuk server</span></td>
