				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: drum of the beast<a name="8419"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 23 03 7:13 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Some explanation :
<br />

<br />
As a lvl 65 Bard, i easily tank the shimmering spirit and the place holder watery servant and icy servant when these are slowed.
<br />

<br />
1) Single pull
<br />
There are several spots for the servants. Easy one are out of water. harder one are in water so everyone will need one EB item. U can lull/pacify all the mobs before pull. There is a spot with 4 servants and Sirens. This is easy to pull there and lull.
<br />

<br />
2) Slow
<br />
with 52% slow,u can tank them so u only need one healer or one shaman for easy fight
<br />

<br />
3)Spawn time
<br />
I dont know if spirit is a rare spawn but it may be if u are only pulling the easy spots. Some spots are in water and others are in one way tunnel under water.
<br />

<br />
4) Advice
<br />
Better have fade in case u didnt single pull or one evacer
<br />
A lot of mobs see invis.
<br />
Some mobs( seahorses ) in water can t go out of water so u just have to run by them
<br />
Some mobs ( Sirens and servants ) can fight in water and on ground so care about pulling these <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
Bleric 65th Vah Shir Bard on Bertoxx</span></td>
